    dc:description "FIGURE 4. A–C, Ceriodaphnia cornigera Chiang, 1977 from Bajiao Lake in Hunan (loc. S6), neonate. A, lateral view. B, ventral view. C, postabdomen. D–I, Scapholeberis smirnovi Garibian et al. 2020 from a fish pond in Hunan (A29), ephippial female. D, lateral view. E, dorsal view. F, head, ventral view. G, ephippium sculpture. H, postabdomen. I, posteroventral angle of valve." ;
